# Force LF for shell scripts and JSON state. Windows clones with
# core.autocrlf=true would otherwise check these out as CRLF, which:
#   * breaks bash (interpreter sees `\r` in shebang/strings)
#   * makes pool.json / snapshot files dirty on every save
#
# Markdown/text default to git's auto handling so editors can normalize freely.

*.sh   text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf

# Binary-ish defaults
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
